      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Half length shot of a seated elderly man wearing a town overcoat and a fez. He is holding a book and he is resting his left arm on a table with a pot plant. A boy wearing urban clothes and a school hat is standing behind him.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Nikola Karastoyanov (1778 - 1874) was a printer, publisher and bookseller, xylographer and engraver on copperplate. Father of the engraver and photographer <ref target="info:fedora/context:vase.pn.df754e76">Anastas Nikolov Stojanović/Karastoyanov</ref>; and grandfather of <ref target="info:fedora/context:vase.pn.c3834c">Ivan Anastasov Karastoyanov</ref>.</ab>
